1065
01:11:36,981 --> 01:11:39,144
- Hey, keep walking.
- No!

1066
01:11:40,217 --> 01:11:42,029
Keep walking.

1067
01:11:42,053 --> 01:11:44,798
Don't let it spook you.

1068
01:11:44,822 --> 01:11:46,800
We all brush against death...

1069
