right next to him.

1090
01:12:29,834 --> 01:12:32,646
Not a technical mistake.
A personal one.

1091
01:12:32,670 --> 01:12:34,748
What do you mean?

1092
01:12:34,772 --> 01:12:36,516
I knew the guy.

1093
01:12:36,540 --> 01:12:38,098
