leave him here alone.

1155
01:17:37,675 --> 01:17:40,053
- Really? Why not?
- They'll kill him.

1156
01:17:40,077 --> 01:17:41,655
Well, perfect.
Better him than us.

1157
01:17:41,679 --> 01:17:44,658
- He's been good to us.
- To you, yeah.

1158
01:17:44,682 --> 01:17:48,161
