1256
01:27:48,318 --> 01:27:49,771
We're all sinners.

1257
01:31:09,686 --> 01:31:11,597
Bad dream?

1258
01:31:13,523 --> 01:31:17,536
Yeah, they're all bad.

1259
01:31:17,560 --> 01:31:19,772
